[0.000, "o", "\u001b[33mв•ӯв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв•®\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[33mв”Ӯ\u001b[0m  \u001b[1;33mIteration Summary\u001b[0m  \u001b[33mв”Ӯ\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[33mв•°в”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв•Ҝ\u001b[0m\r\n"]
[0.001, "o", "\u001b[33mв•ӯв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв”Җв•®\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[33mв”Ӯ\u001b[0m                                                                                                                                                                                                  \u001b[33mв”Ӯ\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[33mв”Ӯ\u001b[0m  Across all three iterations, the dominant trade proposal was to execute zero trades and maintain a 100% cash position. The Portfolio Manager consistently noted that while Microsoft (MSFT)    "]
[0.000, "o", " \u001b[33mв”Ӯ\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[33mв”Ӯ\u001b[0m  generated the only bullish signal, it was untradable due to a critical data error where its price was listed as $0.0.                                                                           \u001b[33mв”Ӯ\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[33mв”Ӯ\u001b[0m                                                                                                                                                                                                  \u001b[33mв”Ӯ\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[33mв”Ӯ\u001b[0m  This missing data repeatedly triggered a hard constraint preventing the execution of buy orders for assets without valid pricing. Additionally, a strict \"no shorting\" constraint prevented     \u001b[33mв”Ӯ\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[33mв”Ӯ\u001b[0m  the system from capitalizing on Meta's (META) bearish signal, as the initial portfolio held zero shares. Apple (AAPL), Nvidia (NVDA), and Alphabet (GOOGL) consistently returned neutral        \u001b[33mв”Ӯ\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[33mв”Ӯ\u001b[0m  signals, which, per the system's rules, precluded deploying new capital into them. The Monitor agent validated thes"]
[0.000, "o", "e zero-trade proposals in every iteration without flagging any violations,   \u001b[33mв”Ӯ\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[33mв”Ӯ\u001b[0m  as no capital was at risk.                                                                                                                                                                      \u001b[33mв”Ӯ\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[33mв”Ӯ\u001b[0m                                                                                                                                                                                                  \u001b[33mв”Ӯ\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[33mв”Ӯ\u001b[0m  The What-If agent raised no counter-arguments or alternative trade scenarios. Instead, it provided strong corroborating critiques, emphasizing that capital preservation is paramount when      \u001b[33mв”Ӯ\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[33mв”Ӯ\u001b[0m  valid pricing data is missing and available assets trade at steep premiums to their intrinsic value. The What-If agent explicitly praised the defensive strategy, noting it perfectly aligned   \u001b[33mв”Ӯ\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[33mв”Ӯ\u001b[0m  with the value investing principle of w"]
[0.000, "o", "aiting for a \"fat pitch\" and demanding a proper margin of safety.                                                                                        \u001b[33mв”Ӯ\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[33mв”Ӯ\u001b[0m                                                                                                                                                                                                  \u001b[33mв”Ӯ\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[33mв”Ӯ\u001b[0m  Ultimately, there was absolute, persistent consensus among all agents throughout the entire optimization loop. With no valid bullish targets and strict constraints against shorting or buying  \u001b[33mв”Ӯ\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[33mв”Ӯ\u001b[0m  neutral assets, the agents unanimously agreed to hold the entire $100,000 balance in cash until accurate pricing data and favorable valuations materialize.                                     \u001b[33mв”Ӯ\u001b[0m\r\n\u001b[33mв”Ӯ\u001b[0m                                                                                                                                                                                         "]
